==Chinese==
===Pronunciation===
====[[Mandarin]]====
[[Pinyin]]: rù xiāng suí sú

====[[Min Nan]]====
[[POJ]]: li̍p-hiong-sûi-sio̍k

===Etymology===
Literally: When entering a village, follow the customs.

===Proverb===
'''[[入]][[乡]][[随]][[俗]]'''

# [[when in Rome, do as the Romans do]].

===Alternate forms===
[[入鄉隨俗]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

===Related terms===
*[[入]][[境]][[随]][[俗]]

